item.title: FreeBSD Office Hours
item.description: FreeBSD Office Hours (https://live.freebsd.org/FreeBSD/officehours/), live.FreeBSD.org 03 December, 2020. On December 3rd at 18:00 UTC we will hold a "FreeBSD Office Hours", an interactive online event where users, contributors, and developers can ask questions or to offer comments. The topic will be "Git Q&A." For more information please see the Office Hours page on the FreeBSD wiki.
